{
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "description": "Developer-loop dashboard \u2014 recent traces, errors, slow queries. Intended for local/dev only. Use Explore drilldowns from each panel.",
  "editable": false,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "HTTP 5xx + 4xx by route (top 10, 5m)",
      "description": "Surfaces routes that are currently erroring — the canonical 'what just broke' panel for a dev loop. 5xx (server-side bug or downstream failure) and 4xx (validation, auth, business-rule reject) are graphed together so a flip from 4xx-dominant to 5xx-dominant during a refactor jumps out.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "VictoriaMetrics"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 12,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "calcs": ["mean", "max"]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (http_route, http_response_status_code) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{http_response_status_code=~\"4..|5..\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{http_response_status_code}} {{http_route}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "HTTP request rate (all routes)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "VictoriaMetrics"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "max"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (http_route) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{http_route}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Oldest open Postgres transaction (s)",
      "description": "Catches the classic dev mistake: code path that opens a transaction but doesn't commit/rollback on every return — the connection lingers, this number climbs. Deadlock rate and rollback rate live on Infra Health (the canonical PG operational view); this panel keeps only the dev-iteration signal so the two dashboards don't double-up.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "VictoriaMetrics"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green"},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 5},
              {"color": "red", "value": 30}
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": ["mean", "max"]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "max(cnpg_backends_max_tx_duration_seconds{datname=\"tbite\"})",
          "legendFormat": "oldest open tx",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Recent traces \u2014 explore via right-click",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "jaeger",
        "uid": "victoria-traces"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "query": "tbite-api",
          "queryType": "search",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Helpful links",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 30
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "- **API**: http://api.tbite.local/healthz\n- **Employee**: http://app.tbite.local\n- **Merchant**: http://merchant.tbite.local\n- **Admin**: http://admin.tbite.local\n- **MinIO**: http://minio.tbite.local\n- **Grafana**: http://grafana.tbite.local\n"
      },
      "targets": []
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "10s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": [
    "dev",
    "local"
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "Dev Loop",
  "uid": "dev-loop",
  "version": 1,
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "System Status",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/d/status",
      "icon": "external link",
      "targetBlank": false
    },
    {
      "title": "Service Health",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/d/oncall-overview",
      "icon": "external link",
      "targetBlank": false
    }
  ]
}
